==Finnish==

===Etymology 1===
Presumably from earlier ''*vapada'', from {{bor|fi|orv|свободь|t=free|pos=adj.}}, from {{der|fi|sla-pro|*svoboda|t=freedom}}.

====Pronunciation====
* {{fi-IPA}}
* {{rhymes|ɑpɑː|lang=fi}}
* {{hyphenation|va|paa|lang=fi}}

====Adjective====
{{fi-adj|vapa|ampi|in}}

# [[free]] {{gloss|not imprisoned or enslaved}}
#: {{ux|fi|Olen '''vapaa''' mies.|I am a '''free''' man.}}
# free {{gloss|unconstrained}}
#: {{ux|fi|Hänelle annettiin '''vapaat''' kädet tehdä, mitä hän haluaa.|He was given '''free''' rein to do whatever he wanted.}}
# free {{gloss|released}}
#: {{ux|fi|Päästimme kanin '''vapaaksi'''.|We set the rabbit '''free'''.}}
# free, [[off]] {{gloss|without obligations}}
#: {{ux|fi|Voit pitää loppupäivän '''vapaata'''.|You can take the rest of the day '''off'''.}}
# [[spare]], free {{gloss|not filled with activity or work}}
#: {{ux|fi|Minulla on paljon '''vapaa'''-aikaa.|I have a lot of '''free''' time.}}
# [[vacant]]
#: {{ux|fi|Istuin on '''vapaa'''.|The seat is '''vacant'''.}}
# [[unmarried]], [[single]]
# [[free-range]] (of, pertaining to, or produced by animals that are allowed to roam freely, rather than being confined indoors)
#: {{ux|fi|Ostan aina '''vapaan''' kanan munia.|I always buy '''free-range''' eggs.}}
# {{lb|fi|linear algebra}} [[linearly independent]] {{gloss|of a set of vectors}}

